        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h2><a></a>PREFACE.</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"figcenter c3\"><$image tooltip=\"\" alt=\"\" source=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/images/OEBPS/4905307567846168275_illus-003.png\"></$image></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>In the literature of all countries there will be found a certain number of works treating especially of love. Everywhere the subject is dealt with differently, and from various points of view. In the present publication it is proposed to give a complete translation of what is considered the standard work on love in <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002460\">Sanscrit</$link> literature, and which is called the 'Vatsyayana Kama Sutra,' or Aphorisms on Love, by Vatsyayana.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>While the introduction will bear with the evidence concerning the date of the writing, and the commentaries written upon it, the chapters following the introduction will give a translation of the work itself. It is, however, advisable to furnish here a brief analysis of works of the same nature, prepared by authors who lived and wrote years after Vatsya had passed away, but who still considered him as a great authority, and always quoted him as the chief guide to Hindoo erotic literature.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Besides the treatise of Vatsyayana the following works on the same subject are procurable in India:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"1\">The Ratirahasya, or secrets of love.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"2\">The Panchasakya, or the five arrows.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"3\">The Smara Pradipa, or the light of love.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"4\">The Ratimanjari, or the garland of love.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000037",
