            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Chapter</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001016\">I</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Observations on Betrothal and Marriage.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001064\">II</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">About creating Confidence in the Girl.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001075\">III</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Courtship, and the manifestations of the feelings by outward signs and deeds.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001087\">IV</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">On things to be done only by the Man, and the acquisition of the Girl thereby. Also what to be done by a Girl to gain over a Man and subject him to her.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001101\">V</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">On the different Forms of Marriage.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>"
        },
