            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Chapter</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001563\">I</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">On the Characteristics of Men and Women, and the reason why Women reject the Addresses of Men. About Men who have Success with Women, and about Women who are easily gained over.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001663\">II</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Of a Courtesan living with a Man as his Wife.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001679\">III</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Of the means of getting Money; of the Signs of a Lover who is beginning to be weary, and of the way to get rid of him.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001758\">IV</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">About a Re-union with a former Lover.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001796\">V</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Of different kinds of Gain.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"tdc\">&quot;</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\"><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001819\">VI</$link>.</td>\n<td class=\"tdl\">Of Gains and Losses, attendant Gains and Losses, and Doubts; and lastly, the different kinds of Courtesans.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>"
        },
