        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"41\">Art of cock fighting, quail fighting and ram fighting.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"42\">Art of teaching parrots and starlings to speak.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"43\">Art of applying perfumed ointments to the body, and of dressing the hair with unguents and perfumes and braiding it.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"44\">The art of understanding writing in cypher, and the writing of words in a peculiar way.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"45\"><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>The art of speaking by changing the forms of words. It is of various kinds. Some speak by changing the beginning and end of words, others by adding unnecessary letters between every syllable of a word, and so on.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000272": {
