            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Having thus acquired learning, a man, with the wealth that he may have gained by gift, conquest, purchase, deposit,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002174\">[14]</$link> or inheritance from his ancestors, should become a householder, and pass the life of a citizen. He should take a house in a city, or large village, or in the vicinity of good men, or in a place which is the resort of many persons. This abode should be situated near some water, and divided into different compartments for different purposes. It should be surrounded by a garden, and also contain two rooms, an outer and an inner one. The inner room should be occupied by the females, while the outer room, balmy with rich perfumes, should contain a bed, soft, agreeable to the sight covered with a clean white cloth, low in the middle part, having garlands and bunches of flowers<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002178\">[15]</$link> upon it, and a canopy above it, and two pillows, one at the top, another at the <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002470\">bottom</$link>. There should be also a sort of couch besides, and at the head of this a sort of stool, on which should be placed the fragrant ointments for the night, as well as flowers, pots containing collyrium and other fragrant substances, things used for perfuming the mouth, and the bark of the common citron tree. Near the couch, on the ground, there should be a pot for spitting, a box containing ornaments, and also a lute hanging from a peg made of the tooth of an elephant, a board for drawing, a pot containing perfume, some books, and some garlands of the yellow amaranth flowers. Not far from the couch, and on the ground, there should be a round seat, a toy cart, and a board for playing with dice; outside the outer room <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>there should be cages of birds,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002182\">[16]</$link> and a separate place for spinning, carving, and such like diversions. In the garden there should be a whirling swing and a common swing, as also a bower of creepers covered with flowers, in which a raised parterre should be made for sitting.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Now the householder having got up in the morning and performed his necessary duties,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002186\">[17]</$link> should wash his teeth, apply a limited quantity of ointments and perfumes to his body, put some ornaments on his person and collyrium on his eyelids and below his eyes, colour his lips with alacktaka,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002190\">[18]</$link> and look at himself in the glass. Having then eaten betel leaves, with other things that give fragrance to the mouth, he should perform his usual business. He should bathe daily, anoint his body with oil every other day, apply a lathering<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002194\">[19]</$link> substance to his body every three days, get his head (including face) shaved every four days, and the other parts of his body every five or ten days.<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002198\">[20]</$link> All these things should be done without fail, and the sweat of the armpits should also be removed. Meals should be taken in the forenoon, in the afternoon, and again at night, according to Charayana. After breakfast, parrots and other birds should be taught to speak, and the fighting of cocks, quails, and rams should follow. A limited time should be devoted to diversions with Pithamardas, Vitas, and Vidushakas,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002202\">[21]</$link> and then should be taken the midday sleep.<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002206\">[22]</$link> After this the householder, having put on his clothes and ornaments, should, during the afternoon, converse with his friends. In the evening there should be singing, and after that the householder, along with his friend, should await in his room, previously decorated and perfumed, the arrival of the woman that may be attached to him, or he may send a female messenger for her, <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>or go for her himself. After her arrival at his house, he and his friend should welcome her, and entertain her with a loving and agreeable conversation. Thus end the duties of the day.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The following are the things to be done occasionally as diversions or amusements.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"1\">Holding festivals<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002210\">[23]</$link> in honour of different Deities.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"2\">Social gatherings of both sexes.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"3\">Drinking parties.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"4\">Picnics.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol><li value=\"5\">Other social diversions.</li></ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ol>\n</ol></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Festivals.</i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>On some particular auspicious day, an assembly of citizens should be convened in the temple of Saraswati.<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002214\">[24]</$link> There the skill of singers, and of others who may have come recently to the town, should be tested, and on the following day they should always be given some rewards. After that they may either be retained or dismissed, according as their performances are liked or not by the assembly. The members of the assembly should act in concert, both in times of distress as well as in times of prosperity, and it is also the duty of these citizens to show hospitality to strangers who may have come to the assembly. What is said above should be <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002472\">understood</$link> to apply to all the other festivals which may be held in honour of the different Deities, according to the present rules.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Social Gatherings.</i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When men of the same age, disposition and talents, fond of the same diversions and with the same degree of education, sit together in company with public women,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002218\">[25]</$link> or in an assembly of <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>citizens, or at the abode of one among themselves, and engage in agreeable discourse with each other, such is called a sitting in company or a social gathering. The subjects of discourse are to be the completion of verses half composed by others, and the testing the knowledge of one another in the various arts. The women who may be the most beautiful, who may like the same things that the men like, and who may have power to attract the minds of others, are here done homage to.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Drinking Parties.</i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Men and women should drink in one another's houses. And here the men should cause the public women to drink, and should then drink themselves, liquors such as the Madhu, Aireya, Sara, and Asawa, which are of bitter and sour taste; also drinks concocted from the barks of various trees, wild fruits and leaves.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Going to Gardens or Picnics.</i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>In the forenoon, men, having dressed themselves should go to gardens on horseback, accompanied by public women and followed by servants. And having done there all the duties of the day, and passed the time in various agreeable diversions, such as the fighting of quails, cocks and rams, and other spectacles, they should return home in the afternoon in the same manner, bringing with them bunches of flowers, &amp;c.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The same also applies to bathing in summer in water from which wicked or dangerous animals have previously been taken out, and which has been built in on all sides.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p class=\"center\"><i>Other Social Diversions.</i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Spending nights playing with dice. Going out on moonlight nights. Keeping the festive day in honour of spring. Plucking the sprouts and fruits of the mangoe trees. Eating<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> the fibres of lotuses. Eating the tender ears of corn. Picnicing in the forests when the trees get their new foliage. The Udakakashvedika or sporting in the water. Decorating each other with the flowers of some trees. Pelting each other with the flowers of the Kadamba tree, and many other sports which may either be known to the whole country, or may be peculiar to particular parts of it. These and similar other amusements should always be carried on by citizens.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The above amusements should be followed by a person who diverts himself alone in company with a courtesan, as well as by a courtesan who can do the same in company with her maid servants or with citizens.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>A Pithamarda<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002222\">[26]</$link> is a man without wealth, alone in the world, whose only property consists of his Mallika,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002226\">[27]</$link> some lathering, substance and a red cloth, who comes from a good country, and who is skilled in all the arts; and by teaching these arts is received in the company of citizens, and in the abode of public women.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>A Vita<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002230\">[28]</$link> is a man who has enjoyed the pleasures of fortune, who is a compatriot of the citizens with whom he associates, who is possessed of the qualities of a householder, who has his wife with him, and who is honoured in the assembly of citizens, and in the abodes of public women, and lives on their means and on them.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>A Vidushaka<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002234\">[29]</$link> (also called a Vaihasaka, <i>i.e.</i>, one who provokes <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>laughter) is a person only acquainted with some of the arts who is a jester, and who is trusted by all.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>These persons are employed in matters of quarrels and reconciliations between citizens and public women.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>This remark applies also to female beggars, to women with <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002474\">their</$link> heads shaved, to adulterous women, and to old public women skilled in all the various arts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Thus a citizen living in his town or village, respected by all, should call on the persons of his own caste who may be worth knowing. He should converse in company and gratify his friends by his society, and obliging others by his assistance in various matters, he should cause them to assist one another in the same way.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>There are some verses on this subject as follows:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>A citizen discoursing, not entirely in the Sanscrit language,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002238\">[30]</$link> nor wholly in the dialects of the country, on various topics in society, obtains great respect. The wise should not resort to a society disliked by the public, governed by no rules, and intent on the destruction of others. But a learned man living in a society which acts according to the wishes of the people, and which has pleasure for its only object is highly respected in this world.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\">\n\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER V.</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h3>ABOUT THE KINDS OF WOMEN RESORTED TO BY THE CITIZENS, AND OF FRIENDS AND MESSENGERS.</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When Kama is practised by men of the four castes according to the rules of the Holy Writ (<i>i.e.</i>, by lawful marriage) with virgins of their own caste, it then becomes a means of acquiring lawful progeny and good fame, and it is not also opposed to the customs of the world. On the contrary the practice of Kama with women of the higher castes, and with those previously enjoyed by others, even though they be of the same caste, is prohibited. But the practice of Kama with women of the lower castes, with women excommunicated from their own caste, with public women, and with women twice married,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002242\">[31]</$link> is neither enjoined nor prohibited. The object of practising Kama with such women is pleasure only.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Nayikas,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002246\">[32]</$link> therefore, are of three kinds, viz., maids, women twice married, and public women. Gonikaputra has expressed an opinion that there is a fourth kind of Nayika, viz., a woman who is resorted to on some special occasion even though she be previously married to another. These special occasions are when a man thinks thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>a</i>). This woman is self-willed, and has been previously enjoyed by many others besides myself. I may, therefore, safely resort to her as to a public woman though she belongs to a higher caste than mine, and in so doing I shall not be violating the ordinances of Dharma.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>b</i>). This is a twice-married woman and has been enjoyed by others before me, there is, therefore, no objection to my resorting to her.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>c</i>). This woman has gained the heart of her great and powerful husband, and exercises a mastery over him, who is a friend of my enemy; if, therefore, she becomes united with me, she will cause her husband to abandon my enemy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>d</i>). This woman will turn the mind of her husband, who is very powerful, in my favour, he being at present disaffected towards me, and intent on doing me some harm.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>e</i>). By making this woman my friend I shall gain the object of some friend of mine, or shall be able to effect the ruin of some enemy, or shall accomplish some other difficult purpose.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>f</i>). By being united with this woman, I shall kill her husband, and so obtain his vast riches which I covet.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>g</i>). The union of this woman with me is not attended with any danger, and will bring me wealth, of which, on account of my poverty and inability to support myself, I am very much in need. I shall, therefore, obtain her vast riches in this way without any difficulty.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>h</i>). This woman loves me ardently, and knows all my weak points, if therefore, I am unwilling to be united with her, she will make my faults public, and thus tarnish my character and reputation. Or she will bring some gross accusation against me, of which it may be hard to clear myself, and I shall be ruined. Or perhaps she will detach from me her husband, who is powerful, and yet under her control, and will unite him to my enemy, or will herself join the latter.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>i</i>). The husband of this woman has violated the chastity of my wives, I shall therefore return that injury by seducing his wives.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>j</i>). By the help of this woman I shall kill an enemy of the king, who has taken shelter with her, and whom I am ordered by the king to destroy.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>k</i>). The woman whom I love is under the control of this woman. I shall, through the influence of the latter, be able to get at the former.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>l</i>). This woman will bring to me a maid, who possesses wealth and beauty, but who is hard to get at, and under the control of another.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Or, lastly, thus:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\"><p>(<i>m</i>). My enemy is a friend of this woman's husband, I shall therefore cause her to join him, and will thus create an enmity between her husband and him.</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"blockquot\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>For these and similar other reasons the wives of other men may be resorted to, but it must be distinctly understood that is only allowed for special reasons, and not for mere carnal desire.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Charayana thinks that under these circumstances there is also a fifth kind of Nayika, viz., a woman who is kept by a minister, and who repairs to him occasionally; or a widow who accomplishes the purpose of a man with the person to whom she resorts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Suvarnanabha adds that a woman who passes the life of an ascetic and in the condition of a widow may be considered as a sixth kind of Nayika.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Ghotakamukha says that the daughter of a public woman, and a female servant, who are still virgins, form a seventh kind of Nayika.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Gonardiya puts forth his doctrine that any woman born of good family, after she has come of age, is an eighth kind of Nayika.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>But these four latter kinds of Nayikas do not differ much from the first four kinds of them, as there is no separate<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> object in resorting to them. Therefore Vatsyayana is of opinion that there are only four kinds of Nayikas, <i>i.e.</i>, the maid, the twice married woman, the public woman, and the woman resorted to for a special purpose.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The following women are not to be enjoyed:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\">A leper.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"2\">A lunatic.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">A woman turned out of caste.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"4\">A woman who reveals secrets.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"5\">A woman who publicly expresses desire for sexual intercourse.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"6\">A woman who is extremely white.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"7\">A woman who is extremely black.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"8\">A bad-smelling woman.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"9\">A woman who is a near relation.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"10\">A woman who is a female friend.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"11\">A woman who leads the life of an ascetic.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"12\">And, lastly, the wife of a relation, of a friend, of a learned Brahman, and of the king.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The followers of Babhravya say that any woman who has been enjoyed by five men is a fit and proper person to be enjoyed. But Gonikaputra is of opinion that even when this is the case, the wives of a relation, of a learned Brahman and of a king should be excepted.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The following are the kind of friends:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\">One who has played with you in the dust, <i>i.e.</i>, in childhood.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"2\">One who is bound by an obligation.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">One who is of the same disposition and fond of the same things.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"4\">One who is a fellow student.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"5\">One who is acquainted with your secrets and faults, and whose faults and secrets are also known to you.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"6\">One who is a child of your nurse.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"7\">One who is brought up with you.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"8\">One who is an hereditary friend.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>These friends should possess the following qualities:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\">They should tell the truth.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"2\">They should not be changed by time.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">They should be favourable to your designs.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"4\">They should be firm.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"5\"><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>They should be free from covetousness.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"6\">They should not be capable of being gained over by others.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"7\">They should not reveal your secrets.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Charayana says that citizens form friendship with washermen, barbers, cowherds, florists, druggists, betel-leaf sellers, tavern keepers, beggars, Pithamardas, Vitas and Vidushekas, as also with the wives of all these people.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\">A messenger should possess the following qualities:—</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"2\">Skilfulness.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">Boldness.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"4\">Knowledge of the intention of men by their outward signs.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"5\">Absence of confusion, <i>i.e.</i>, no shyness.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"6\">Knowledge of the exact meaning of what others do or say.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
