        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>The action in each case is denoted by the meaning of the word which stands for it.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(1). When a man under some pretext or other goes in front or alongside of a woman and touches her body with his own, it is called the &quot;touching embrace.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). When a woman in a lonely place bends down, as if to pick up something, and pierces, as it were, a man sitting or standing, with her breasts, and the man in return takes hold of them, it is called a &quot;piercing embrace.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The above two kinds of embrace takes place only between persons who do not, as yet, speak freely with each other.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When two lovers are walking slowly together, either in the dark, or in a place of public resort, or in a lonely place, and rub their bodies against each other, it is called a &quot;rubbing embrace.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(4). When on the above occasion one of them presses the other's body forcibly against a wall or pillar, it is called a &quot;pressing embrace.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>These two last embraces are peculiar to those who know the intentions of each other.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>At the time of the meeting the four following kinds of embrace are used, viz.:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\"><i>Jataveshtitaka</i>, or the twining of a creeper.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000590",
