        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(1). When a girl only touches the mouth of her lover with her own, but does not herself do anything, it is called the &quot;nominal kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). When a girl, setting aside her bashfulness a little, wishes to touch the lip that is pressed into her mouth, and<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> with that object moves her lower lip, but not the upper one, it is called the &quot;throbbing kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When a girl touches her lover's lip with her tongue, and having shut her eyes, places her hands on those of her lover, it is called the &quot;touching kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Other authors describe four other kinds of kisses, viz.:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000639",
