        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(1). When the lips of two lovers are brought into direct contact with each other, it is called a &quot;straight kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). When the heads of two lovers are bent towards each other, and when so bent kissing takes place, it is called a &quot;bent kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When one of them turns up the face of the other by holding the head and chin, and then kissing, it is called a &quot;turned kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(4). Lastly, when the lower lip is pressed with much force, it is called a &quot;pressed kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>There is also a fifth kind of kiss called the &quot;greatly pressed kiss,&quot; which is effected by taking hold of the lower lip between two fingers, and then after touching it with the tongue, pressing it with great force with the lip.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>As regards kissing, a wager may be laid as to which will get hold of the lips of the other first. If the woman loses, she should pretend to cry, should keep her lover off by shaking her hands, and turn away from him and dispute with him, saying &quot;let another wager be laid.&quot; If she loses this a second time, she should appear doubly distressed, and when her lover is off his guard or asleep, she should get hold of his lower lip, and hold it in her teeth, so that it should not slip away, and then she should laugh, make a loud noise, deride him, dance about, and say whatever she likes in a joking way, moving her eyebrows, and rolling her eyes. Such are the wagers and quarrels as far as kissing is concerned, but the same may be applied with regard to the pressing or scratching with the nails and fingers, biting and striking. All these, however, are only peculiar to men and women of intense passion.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a man kisses the upper lip of a woman, while she in return kisses his lower lip, it is called the &quot;kiss of the upper lip.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When one of them takes both the lips of the other between<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> his or her own, it is called &quot;a clasping kiss.&quot; A woman, however, only takes this kind of kiss from a man who has no moustache. And on the occasion of this kiss, if one of them touches the teeth, the tongue, and the palate of the other, with his or her tongue, it is called the &quot;fighting of the tongue.&quot; In the same way, the pressing of the teeth of the one against the mouth of the other is to be practised.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Kissing is of four kinds, viz., moderate, contracted, pressed, and soft, according to the different parts of the body which are kissed, for different kinds of kisses are appropriate for different parts of the body.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a woman looks at the face of her lover while he is asleep, and kisses it to show her intention or desire, <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002482\">it</$link> is called a &quot;kiss that kindles love.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a woman kisses her lover while he is engaged in business, or while he is quarrelling with her, or while he is looking at something else, so that his mind may be turned away, it is called a &quot;kiss that turns away.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a lover coming home late at night kisses his beloved, who is asleep or in bed, in order to show her his desire, it is called a &quot;kiss that awakens.&quot; On such an occasion the woman may pretend to be asleep at the time of her lover's arrival, so that she may know his intention and obtain respect from him.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a person kisses the reflection of the person he loves in a mirror, in water, or on a wall, it is called a &quot;kiss showing the intention.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a person kisses a child sitting on his lap, or a picture, or an image, or figure, in the presence of the person beloved by him, it is called a &quot;transferred kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When at night at a theatre, or in an assembly of caste men, a man coming up to a woman kisses a finger of her hand if she be standing, or a toe of her foot if she be sitting, or when a woman is shampooing her lover's body, places her face on his thigh (as if she was sleepy) so as to inflame his passion, and kisses his thigh or great toe, it is called a &quot;demonstrative kiss.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>There is also a verse on the subject as follows:—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>&quot;Whatever things may be done by one of the lovers to the other, the same should be returned by the other, <i>i.e.</i>, if the woman kisses him he should kiss her in return, if she strikes him he should also strike her in return.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\">\n\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER IV.</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h3>ON PRESSING, OR MARKING, OR SCRATCHING WITH THE NAILS.</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When love becomes intense, pressing with the nails or scratching the body with them is practised, and it is done on the following occasions: On the first visit; at the time of setting out on a journey; on the return from a journey; at the time when an angry lover is reconciled; and lastly when the woman is intoxicated.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>But pressing with the nails is not an usual thing except with those who are intensely passionate, <i>i.e.</i>, full of passion. It is employed together with biting, by those to whom the practice is agreeable.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Pressing with the nails is of the eight following kinds, according to the forms of the marks which are produced, viz.:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000672",
