            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">Large.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Large nails, which give grace to the hands, and attract the<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> hearts of women from their appearance, are possessed by the Bengalees.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Small nails, which can be used in various ways, and are to be applied only with the object of giving pleasure, are possessed by the people of the southern districts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Middling nails, which contain the properties of both the above kinds, belong to the people of the Maharashtra.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(1). When a person presses the chin, the breasts, the lower lip, or the jaghana of another so softly that no scratch or mark is left, but only the hair on the body becomes erect from the touch of the nails, and the nails themselves make a sound, it is called a &quot;sounding or pressing with the nails.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>This pressing is used in the case of a young girl when her lover shampoos her, scratches her head, and wants to trouble or frighten her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). The curved mark with the nails, which is impressed on the neck and the breasts, <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002488\">is</$link> called the &quot;half moon.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When the half moons are impressed opposite to each other, it is called a &quot;circle.&quot; This mark with the nails is generally made on the navel, the small cavities about the buttocks, and on the joints of the thigh.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(4). A mark in the form of a small line, and which can be made on any part of the body, is called a &quot;line.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(5). This same line, when it is curved, and made on the breast, is called a &quot;tiger's nail.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(6). When a curved mark is made on the breast by means of the five nails, it is called a &quot;peacock's foot.&quot; This mark is made with the object of being praised, for it requires a great deal of skill to make it properly.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(7). When five marks with the nails are made close to one another near the nipple of the breast, it is called &quot;the jump of a hare.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(8). A mark made on the breast or on the hips in the form of a leaf of the blue lotus, is called the &quot;leaf of a blue lotus.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a person is going on a journey, and makes a mark on the thighs, or on the breast, it is called a &quot;token of remembrance.&quot; On such an occasion three or four lines are impressed close to one another with the nails.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Here ends the marking with the nails. Marks of other kinds than the above may also be made with the nails, for the<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> ancient authors say, that as there are innumerable degrees of skill among men (the practice of this art being known to all), so there are innumerable ways of making these marks. And as pressing or marking with the nails is independent of love, no one can say with certainty how many different kinds of marks with the nails do actually exist. The reason of this is, Vatsyayana says, that as variety is necessary in love, so love is to be produced by means of variety. It is on this account that courtezans, who are well acquainted with various ways and means, become so desirable, for if variety is sought in all the arts and amusements, such as archery and others, how much more should it be sought after in the present case.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The marks of the nails should not be made on married women, but particular kinds of marks may be made on their private parts for the remembrance and increase of love.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>There are also some verses on the subject, as follows:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>&quot;The love of a woman who sees the marks of nails on the private parts of her body, even though they are old and almost worn out, becomes again fresh and new. If there be no marks of nails to remind a person of the passages of love, then love is lessened in the same way as when no union takes place for a long time.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Even when a stranger sees at a distance a young woman with the marks of nails on her breast,<a></a><$link class=\"fnanchor pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002266\">[37]</$link> he is filled with love and respect for her.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>A man, also, who carries the marks of nails and teeth on some parts of his body, influences the mind of a woman, even though it be ever so firm. In short, nothing tends to increase love so much as the effects of marking with the nails, and biting.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\">\n\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER V.</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h3>ON BITING, AND THE MEANS TO BE EMPLOYED WITH REGARD TO WOMEN OF DIFFERENT COUNTRIES.</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>All the places that can be kissed, are also the places that can be bitten, except the upper lip, the interior of the mouth, and the eyes.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The qualities of good teeth are as follows: They should be equal, possessed of a pleasing brightness, capable of being coloured, of proper proportions, unbroken, and with sharp ends.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The defects of teeth on the other hand are, that they are blunt, protruding from the gums, rough, soft, large, and loosely set.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The following are the different kinds of biting, viz.:</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"1\">The hidden bite.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"2\">The swollen bite.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">The point.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"4\">The line of points.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"5\">The coral and the jewel.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"6\">The line of jewels.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"7\">The broken cloud.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"8\">The biting of the boar.</li></ul></div>"
