            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). When the skin is pressed down on both sides, it is called the &quot;swollen bite.&quot;</p></div>"
