        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When a small portion of the skin is bitten with two teeth only, it is called the &quot;point.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(4). When such small portions of the skin are bitten with all the teeth, it is called the &quot;line of points.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(5). The biting which is done by bringing together the<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> teeth and the lips, is called the &quot;coral and the jewel.&quot; The lip is the coral, and the teeth the jewel.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(6). When biting is done with all the teeth, it is called the &quot;line of jewels.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(7). The biting which consists of unequal risings in a circle, and which comes from the space between the teeth, is called the &quot;broken cloud.&quot; This is impressed on the breasts.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(8). The biting which consists of many broad rows of marks near to one another, and with red intervals, is called the &quot;biting of a boar.&quot; This is impressed on the breasts and the shoulders; and these two last modes of biting are peculiar to persons of intense passion.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The lower lip is the place on which the &quot;hidden bite,&quot; the &quot;swollen bite,&quot; and the &quot;point&quot; are made; again the &quot;swollen bite,&quot; and the &quot;coral and the jewel&quot; bite are done on the cheek. Kissing, pressing with the nails, and biting are the ornaments of the left cheek, and when the word cheek is used it is to be understood as the left cheek.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Both the &quot;line of points&quot; and the &quot;line of jewels&quot; are to be impressed on the throat, the arm pit, and the joints of the thighs; but the &quot;line of points&quot; alone is to be impressed on the forehead and the thighs.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The marking with the nails, and the biting of the following things, viz., an ornament of the forehead, an ear ornament, a bunch of flowers, a betel leaf, or a tamala leaf, which are worn by, or belong to the woman that is beloved, are signs of the desire of enjoyment.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Here end the different kinds of biting.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\">\n\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>In the affairs of love a man should do such things as are agreeable to the women of different countries.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of the central countries (<i>i.e.</i>, between the Ganges and the Jumna) are noble in their character, not accustomed to disgraceful practices, and dislike pressing the nails and biting.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of the Balhika country are gained over by striking.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Avantika are fond of foul pleasures, and have not good manners.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>The women of the Maharashtra are fond of practising the sixty-four arts, they utter low and harsh words, and like to be spoken to in the same way, and have an impetuous desire of enjoyment.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Pataliputra (<i>i.e.</i>, the modern Patna) are of the same nature as the women of the Maharashtra, but show their likings only in secret.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of the Dravida country, though they are rubbed and pressed about at the time of sexual enjoyment, have a slow fall of semen, that is they are very slow in the act of coition.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Vanavasi are moderately passionate, they go through every kind of enjoyment, cover their bodies, and abuse those who utter low, mean and harsh words.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Avanti hate kissing, marking with the nails, and biting, but they have a fondness for various kinds of sexual union.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000764": {
