            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Malwa like embracing and kissing, but not wounding, and they are gained over by striking.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Abhira, and those of the country about the Indus and five rivers (<i>i.e.</i>, the Punjab), are gained over by the Auparishtaka or mouth congress.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of Aparatika are full of passion, and make slowly the sound &quot;Sit.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
