            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The women of the Audhra country have tender bodies, they are fond of enjoyment, and have a liking for voluptuous pleasures.</p></div>"
