        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\"><li value=\"3\">The position of the wife of Indra.</li></ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><ul class=\"c4\">\n</ul></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(1). When she lowers her head and raises her middle parts, it is called the &quot;widely opened position.&quot; At such a time the man should apply some unguent, so as to make the entrance easy.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(2). When she raises her thighs and keeps them wide apart and engages in congress, it is called the &quot;yawning position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>(3). When she places her thighs with her legs doubled on them upon her sides, and thus engages in congress, it is called the position of Indrani, and this is learnt only by practice. The position is also useful in the case of the &quot;highest congress.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The &quot;clasping position&quot; is used in &quot;low congress,&quot; and in the &quot;lowest congress,&quot; together with the &quot;pressing position,&quot; the &quot;twining position&quot;, and the &quot;mare's position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the legs of both the male and the female are<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> stretched straight out over each other, it is called the &quot;clasping position.&quot; It is of two kinds, the side position and the supine position, according to the way in which they lie down. In the side position the male should invariably lie on his left side, and cause the woman to lie on her right side, and this rule is to be observed in lying down with all kinds of women.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When, after congress has begun in the clasping position, the woman presses her lover with her thighs, it is called the &quot;pressing position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the woman places one of her thighs across the thigh of her lover, it is called the &quot;twining position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a woman forcibly holds in her yoni the lingam after it is in, it is called the &quot;mare's position.&quot; This is learnt by practice only, and is chiefly found among the women of the Andra country.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The above are the different ways of lying down, mentioned by Babhravya; Suvarnanabha, however, gives the following in addition.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the female raises both of her thighs straight up, it is called the &quot;rising position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When she raises both of her legs, and places them on her lover's shoulders, it is called the &quot;yawning position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the legs are contracted, and thus held by the lover before his bosom, it is called the &quot;pressed position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When only one of her legs is stretched out, it is called the &quot;half pressed position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the woman places one of her legs on her lover's shoulder, and stretches the other out, and then places the latter on his shoulder, and stretches out the other, and continues to do so alternately, it is called the &quot;splitting of a bamboo.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When one of her legs is placed on the head, and the other is stretched out, it is called the &quot;fixing of a nail.&quot; This is learnt by practice only.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When both the legs of the woman are contracted, and placed on her stomach, it is called the &quot;crab's position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the thighs are raised and placed one upon the other, it is called the &quot;packed position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When the shanks are placed one upon the other, it is called the &quot;lotus-like position.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>When a man, during congress, turns round, and enjoys the woman without leaving her, while she embraces him round the back all the time, it is called the &quot;turning position,&quot; and is learnt only by practice.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Thus says Suvarnanabha, these different ways of lying down, sitting, and standing should be practised in water, because it is easy to do so therein. But Vatsyayana is of opinion that congress in water is improper, because it is prohibited by the religious law.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a man and a woman support themselves on each other's bodies, or on a wall, or pillar, and thus while standing engage in congress, it is called the &quot;supported congress.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a man supports himself against a wall, and the woman, sitting on his hands joined together and held underneath her, throws her arms round his neck, and putting her thighs alongside his waist, moves herself by her feet, which are touching the wall against which the man is leaning, it is called the &quot;suspended congress.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a woman stands on her hands and feet like a quadruped, and her lover mounts her like a bull, it is called the &quot;congress of a cow.&quot; At this time everything that is ordinarily done on the bosom should be done on the back.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>In the same way can be carried on the congress of a dog, the congress of a goat, the congress of a deer, the forcible mounting of an ass, the congress of a cat, the jump of a tiger, the pressing of an elephant, the rubbing of a boar, and the mounting of a horse. And in all these cases the characteristics of these different animals should be manifested by acting like them.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a man enjoys two women at the same time, both of whom love him equally, it is called the &quot;united congress.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>When a man enjoys many women altogether, it is called the &quot;congress of a herd of cows.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The following kinds of congress, viz., sporting in water, or the congress of an elephant with many female elephants, which is said to take place only in the water, the congress of a collection of goats, the congress of a collection of deer, take place in imitation of these animals.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>In Gramaneri many young men enjoy a woman that may be married to one of them, either one after the other, or at<a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a> the same time. Thus one of them holds her, another enjoys her, a third uses her mouth, a fourth holds her middle part, and in this way they go on enjoying her several parts alternately.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The same things can be done when several men are sitting in company with one courtesan, or when one courtesan is alone with many men. In the same way this can be done by the women of the King's harem when they accidentally get hold of a man.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>The people in the Southern countries have also a congress in the anus, that is called the &quot;lower congress.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>Thus ends the various kinds of congress. There are also two verses on the subject as follows.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p>&quot;An ingenious person should multiply the kinds of congress after the fashion of the different kinds of beasts and of birds. For these different kinds of congress, performed according to the usage of each country, and the liking of each individual, generate love, friendship, and respect in the hearts of women.&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\">\n\n</div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><p><a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h2><a></a>CHAPTER VII.</h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><h3>OF THE VARIOUS MODES OF STRIKING, AND OF THE SOUNDS APPROPRIATE TO THEM.</h3></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000000824",
