        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001446\"><span class=\"label\">[59]</span></$link> The wife of the sage Gautama, she was seduced by Indra the king of the Gods.</p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001446\"><span class=\"label\">[60]</span></$link> The heroine of one of the best, if not the best, of Hindoo plays, and the best known in Sanscrit dramatic literature. It was first brought to notice by Sir William Jones, and has been well and poetically translated by Dr. Monier Williams under the title of Sakoontala, or the lost ring, an Indian drama, translated into English prose and verse from the Sanscrit of Kalidasa.</p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\">\n</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><a></a><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000001452\"><span class=\"label\">[61]</span></$link> It is presumed that something like the following French verses are intended.</p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><span class=\"c11\">Quand on a <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002560\">juré</$link> le plus <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002562\">profond</$link> hommage</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\"><a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002564\">Voulez-vous qu'infidè</$link> le on change de <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002566\">langage</$link></span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Vous <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002568\">seule</$link> captive mon esprit <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002570\">ou</$link> mon cœur</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Que je puisse dans vos bras seuls <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002572\">goûter</$link> le bonheur;</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Je voudrais, mais en vain, que mon cœur en <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002574\">délire</$link></span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Couche <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002576\">où</$link> ce papier n'oserait vous dire.</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Avec soin, de ces vers lisez leur premiers mots,</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Vous verrez quel <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002578\">remède</$link> il faut <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002580\">à</$link> tous mes maux.</span><br></p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p>Or these:</p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\"><p><span class=\"c11\">Quand on vous voit, on vous aime;</span><br>\n<span class=\"c11\">Quand on vous aime, <a></a><$link class=\"correction pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002582\">où vous voit-on</$link>.</span><br></p></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/ca7bc903db05ca3e/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-e24e33 twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-ee4fbb twpub-ca7bc903db05ca3e-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"footnotes\"><div class=\"footnote\">\n</div></div></div>"
        },
